data.description: Country Breeze Estates! Well maintained home with the following improvements paint 2023, Roof 2020, Hot Water Heater 2017, Impact Windows and Front Door 2020, Tile in kitchen, laundry room, and primary bathroom. The backyard is fenced and there is a slab in place where shed used to stand. ALL appliances stay this includes washer, dryer, and refrigerator. The home also has a termite bond in place and seller is offering $3000 for toward new carpet or towards buyers closing costs. NO HOA Less than ten miles to the beach and all the fun the gulf has to offer. Viewing appointments now being taken!
